{"tid":2066651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"監警會：反送中至今有1844宗投訴 其中兩宗黑警講粗口投訴成立 涉事黑警已被⋯⋯⋯訓逾","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:39:45.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec7f88e56c7c906b587c2524a23a57f1a836e72","tid":2066651,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"監警會今午開會，警方公佈涉及反送中的警察投訴數字。截止2020年6月5日，警察投訴課共收到1,844宗有關投訴，其中須匯報投訴佔601宗，而須知會投訴則有1243宗。<br />\n<br />\n其中有兩宗涉及使用粗言穢語的投訴成立，分別為有警員於去年10月14日和9月5日清場時以粗口辱罵市民「行得慢」，涉事警員已被訓諭。俞又補充指，601宗須匯報投訴中，有23％由現場記者作出、27％由被捕人士作出，其餘五成為其他市民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074589&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=d1a82fe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074589&h=07e998cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074589</a>"},{"pid":"c4866e0b1b253933eafaca382bb5c55193ce66b7","tid":2066651,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"80b4865c6410006a3c9d36ad1c6cae1b93a35135","tid":2066651,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"我無錯,係你地錯"},{"pid":"92363b657ceb1e23821d080022e0a6f4558e3cf1","tid":2066651,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928443a0be59c6b53465ab61742e161e29335be4","tid":2066651,"uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"另一方面<br />\n<br />\n去年 11 月 10 日，網民發起「八區開花」示威活動，期間一名 51 歲男子被指於旺角指罵警方「<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母，死差佬</span></span></strong>，我頭先無喇喇食咗兩個催淚彈」。他否認一項<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><s